::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe chuckles, taking a step back. This Maximal was obvioustly hoping 
for his pride to take over. DeathScythe, being an assassin, didn't care which 
way he killed his victim, as long as the bot is dead.

"Foolish Maximal. I don't care how you die," he says in his deadly whisper as 
he fires his gun again, the bolt heading for Lunarpine's chest.
